#: src/app/navigation-patterns/modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom-back-hidden.tsx:38
msgid "「ヘッダーをタイトルだけにし、閉じる動線は本文に集約する」スタイル。iOS の swipe down が 使える前提なら自然に成立する一方、`gestureEnabled: false` を併用する場合は本文の閉じる ボタンが唯一の dismiss 経路になるため、必ず到達可能な位置に配置すること。"
msgstr "A \"header is title-only, with all dismiss affordances consolidated in the body\" style. This works naturally when iOS swipe down is available, but when combined with `gestureEnabled: false`, the body's Close button becomes the only dismiss path — so place it where it is guaranteed to be reachable."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom-back-hidden.tsx:37
msgid "「ヘッダーをタイトルだけにする」スタイル。`gestureEnabled: false` と headerBackVisible: false を併用する場合は、本文の閉じるボタンが唯一の dismiss 経路になるため必ず到達 可能な位置に配置する。"
msgstr "A \"header is title-only\" style. When combining `gestureEnabled: false` with `headerBackVisible: false`, the body's Close button becomes the only dismiss path — place it where it is guaranteed to be reachable."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/modal/in-tab.tsx:32
msgid "「閉じる」ボタン、iOS の swipe down、Android の戻る操作で閉じる。Android ではタブバー越しに見ても card push と区別がつかなくなりやすい点が on-root 版との差分。"
msgstr "Dismiss via the Close button, iOS swipe down, or Android back navigation. On Android, the modal tends to be visually indistinguishable from a card push even with the tab bar in view — that's the differentiator versus the on-root variant."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/modal/in-tab-slide-from-bottom.tsx:29
msgid "「閉じる」ボタン、iOS の swipe down、Android の戻る操作で閉じる。animation 未指定の in-tab 版 (Android は右スライド) との差分を見比べると分かりやすい。"
msgstr "Dismiss via the Close button, iOS swipe down, or Android back navigation. Comparing against the in-tab variant with `animation` unspecified (slide-in from the right on Android) makes the difference easy to see."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/modal/on-root.tsx:34
msgid "「閉じる」ボタン、iOS の swipe down、Android の戻る操作で閉じる。ルート版は、Android で animation 未指定だとタブバーが消えた push 同様の遷移になり、in-tab 版の「Android push と区別がつかない」と挙動が近づく。"
msgstr "Dismiss via the Close button, iOS swipe down, or Android back navigation. On the root variant with `animation` unspecified, Android shows a push-like transition that hides the tab bar, which converges visually with the in-tab variant's \"indistinguishable from a card push\" behavior."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom.tsx:34
msgid "「閉じる」ボタン、iOS の swipe down、Android の戻る操作で閉じる。同じ on-root の animation 未指定版 (Android は右スライド) と見比べると slide_from_bottom の効果が 分かりやすい。"
msgstr "Dismiss via the Close button, iOS swipe down, or Android back navigation. Comparing against the on-root variant with `animation` unspecified (slide-in from the right on Android) makes the effect of `slide_from_bottom` easy to see."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/index.tsx:34
#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/modal/index.tsx:34
msgid "`animation: slide_from_bottom` で両 OS を下からスライドに統一した上で、ヘッダー左の戻る要素を 3 通りに切り替えたサンプル。on-root はタブバーごと覆う / in-tab は Android がタブ内、の挙動差も 同時に確認できる。"
msgstr "Samples that unify the transition to a bottom slide on both OSes via `animation: slide_from_bottom` and switch the back element on the left of the header through three variants. The behavior difference between on-root (covers the tab bar) and in-tab (Android stays in the tab) can be inspected at the same time."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/modal/in-tab-slide-from-bottom-close.tsx:16
msgid "`headerBackIcon` (type: image, source: PNG) でネイティブの back button のグリフ画像を 差し替える。modal なので navigation header の戻る自体出ないことが多く、影響は限定的。"
msgstr "Swap the native back button's glyph image via `headerBackIcon` (type: image, source: PNG). Since this is a modal, the navigation header's back element often isn't shown to begin with, so the visual impact is limited."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom-close.tsx:18
msgid "`headerBackIcon` (type: image, source: PNG) でネイティブの back button のグリフ画像を 差し替える。modal なのでもともと iOS の navigation header の戻るは出ないことが多く、 差し替えても表示への影響は限定的。"
msgstr "Swap the native back button's glyph image via `headerBackIcon` (type: image, source: PNG). Since this is a modal, iOS's navigation header back element often isn't shown in the first place, so swapping it has limited visual impact."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/in-tab-slide-from-bottom-close.tsx:16
msgid "`headerBackIcon` でネイティブ back button のグリフ画像を差し替える。fullScreenModal は UIModalPresentationFullScreen で全画面を覆う。"
msgstr "Swap the native back button's glyph image via `headerBackIcon`. `fullScreenModal` covers the entire screen with UIModalPresentationFullScreen."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom-close.tsx:18
msgid "`headerBackIcon` でネイティブの back button のグリフ画像を差し替える。 fullScreenModal は UIKit の UIModalPresentationFullScreen で全画面を覆う。"
msgstr "Swap the native back button's glyph image via `headerBackIcon`. `fullScreenModal` covers the entire screen with UIKit's UIModalPresentationFullScreen."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom-back-hidden.tsx:24
msgid "`headerBackVisible: false` で Toolbar の navigationIcon が消える。dismiss は OS の戻る 操作 / システムジェスチャー / 画面内の閉じるボタンが必要。slide_from_bottom により下から スライドして全画面を覆う見た目は同じだが、ヘッダー左が完全に空になる。"
msgstr "Setting `headerBackVisible: false` removes the Toolbar's navigationIcon. Dismissal requires the OS back action, system gesture, or an in-screen Close button. The look of `slide_from_bottom` sliding up to cover the full screen is unchanged, but the left side of the header becomes completely empty."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/modal/in-tab-slide-from-bottom-back-hidden.tsx:16
msgid "`headerBackVisible: false` でヘッダー左の戻る/閉じる要素が出ない。dismiss は swipe down または画面内の閉じるボタンに頼る形。"
msgstr "Setting `headerBackVisible: false` hides the back/close element on the left of the header. Dismissal relies on swipe down or an in-screen Close button."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom-back-hidden.tsx:18
msgid "`headerBackVisible: false` でヘッダー左の要素が出ない。`gestureEnabled: false` と 組み合わせると swipe down も無効化されるため、画面内の閉じるボタンが唯一の dismiss 経路になる。"
msgstr "Setting `headerBackVisible: false` hides the element on the left of the header. When combined with `gestureEnabled: false`, swipe down is also disabled, leaving the in-screen Close button as the only dismiss path."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/in-tab-slide-from-bottom-back-hidden.tsx:16
msgid "`headerBackVisible: false` でヘッダー左の要素が出ない。`gestureEnabled: false` と 組み合わせると、画面内の閉じるボタンが唯一の dismiss 経路。"
msgstr "Setting `headerBackVisible: false` hides the element on the left of the header. When combined with `gestureEnabled: false`, the in-screen Close button becomes the only dismiss path."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom-back-hidden.tsx:18
msgid "`headerBackVisible: false` を指定するとヘッダー左の戻る/閉じる要素が出ない。modal の dismiss は swipe down または画面内の閉じるボタンに頼る形になる。"
msgstr "Specifying `headerBackVisible: false` hides the back/close element on the left of the header. Dismissing the modal then relies on swipe down or an in-screen Close button."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/modal/in-tab-slide-from-bottom-close.tsx:35
msgid "`headerLeft` で React Component を返す方式と違い、ネイティブ標準の navigation icon slot を 使うので位置・余白が完全に揃う。代償として PNG (24/48/72dp) を同梱する必要がある。"
msgstr "Unlike the approach of returning a React Component from `headerLeft`, this uses the native standard navigation icon slot, so position and spacing line up perfectly. The trade-off is that PNG assets (24/48/72dp) must be bundled with the project."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/form-sheet/on-root.tsx:40
msgid ""
"Android の formSheet は CoordinatorLayout 上の BottomSheetBehavior として実装される。シート内に ScrollView を置く場合は `nestedScrollEnabled` を true にしてシートの drag と nested scroll を連携させる必要がある (詳細: react-native-screens#2687)。\n"
"\n"
"さらに RN 0.83 の Android ScrollView には「コンテンツの実高さが ScrollView より短い場合、OnInterceptTouchEvent が常に false を返し nested scroll event を一切 dispatch しない」既知の挙動があり、シート内コンテンツが領域に 収まる場合は下スワイプによるシートの dismiss が動かなくなる。RN 側のフィックス (facebook/react-native#55239) は `useNestedScrollViewAndroid` feature flag 経由で RN 0.84 以降に入る見込み。\n"
"\n"
"そのため SDK 55 ではシート内のコンテンツがシート高さを上回るボリュームに なるよう設計するか、grabber や明示的な閉じるボタンを必ず併設するのが安全。 このサンプル画面はその制約を満たすためにこのメモ自体でコンテンツを伸ばして いる。"
msgstr ""
"On Android, formSheet is implemented as a BottomSheetBehavior on top of CoordinatorLayout. If you put a ScrollView inside the sheet, you need to set `nestedScrollEnabled` to true so that sheet drag and nested scroll are linked together (details: react-native-screens#2687).\n"
"\n"
"There is also a known behavior in RN 0.83's Android ScrollView: when the content's actual height is shorter than the ScrollView, `OnInterceptTouchEvent` always returns false and no nested scroll event is dispatched at all. As a result, when sheet content fits within the visible area, dismissing the sheet via downward swipe stops working. The RN-side fix (facebook/react-native#55239) is expected to land in RN 0.84 or later behind the `useNestedScrollViewAndroid` feature flag.\n"
"\n"
"On SDK 55, the safe approach is therefore to either design sheet content so it overflows the sheet height, or always pair the sheet with a grabber or an explicit close button. This sample screen extends content with this note itself in order to satisfy that constraint."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/form-sheet/in-tab.tsx:46
msgid ""
"Android の formSheet は CoordinatorLayout 上の BottomSheetBehavior として実装される。シート内に ScrollView を置く場合は `nestedScrollEnabled` を true にしてシートの drag と nested scroll を連携させる必要がある (詳細: react-native-screens#2687)。\n"
"\n"
"さらに RN 0.83 の Android ScrollView には「コンテンツの実高さが ScrollView より短い場合、OnInterceptTouchEvent が常に false を返し nested scroll event を一切 dispatch しない」既知の挙動があり、シート内コンテンツが領域に収まる 場合は下スワイプによるシートの dismiss が動かなくなる。RN 側のフィックス (facebook/react-native#55239) は `useNestedScrollViewAndroid` feature flag 経由で RN 0.84 以降に入る見込み。\n"
"\n"
"そのため SDK 55 ではシート内のコンテンツがシート高さを上回るボリュームに なるよう設計するか、grabber や明示的な閉じるボタンを必ず併設するのが安全。 このサンプル画面はその制約を満たすためにこのメモ自体でコンテンツを伸ばして いる。"
msgstr ""
"On Android, formSheet is implemented as a BottomSheetBehavior on top of CoordinatorLayout. If you put a ScrollView inside the sheet, you need to set `nestedScrollEnabled` to true so that sheet drag and nested scroll are linked together (details: react-native-screens#2687).\n"
"\n"
"There is also a known behavior in RN 0.83's Android ScrollView: when the content's actual height is shorter than the ScrollView, `OnInterceptTouchEvent` always returns false and no nested scroll event is dispatched at all. As a result, when sheet content fits within the visible area, dismissing the sheet via downward swipe stops working. The RN-side fix (facebook/react-native#55239) is expected to land in RN 0.84 or later behind the `useNestedScrollViewAndroid` feature flag.\n"
"\n"
"On SDK 55, the safe approach is therefore to either design sheet content so it overflows the sheet height, or always pair the sheet with a grabber or an explicit close button. This sample screen extends content with this note itself in order to satisfy that constraint."

