msgid "transparentModal"
msgstr "transparentModal"

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/contained-modal/in-tab.tsx:16
msgid "UIModalPresentationCurrentContext で表示される。`definesPresentationContext: true` を持つ最も近い祖先 view controller (タブ内 Stack の Navigator) の bounds 内に 重なる。本サンプルはホームタブの内側 Stack 配下に配置しているため、開いてもタブバーが 残ったままになるのが観察できる ── これが containedModal の本来期待される挙動。 swipe down では閉じない (UIKit の `UIModalPresentationCurrentContext` 自体が sheet ジェスチャーを持たないため)。ただしこれは React Navigation 公式が明示的に保証している挙動ではない点に注意。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationCurrentContext. Overlays within the bounds of the closest ancestor view controller that has `definesPresentationContext: true` (the in-tab Stack's Navigator). This sample is placed under the in-tab Stack on the Home tab, so opening it keeps the tab bar visible — this is the originally expected behavior of containedModal. Swipe down does not dismiss it (because UIKit's `UIModalPresentationCurrentContext` itself does not provide a sheet gesture). Note however that this behavior is not explicitly guaranteed by React Navigation."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/contained-modal/on-root.tsx:18
msgid "UIModalPresentationCurrentContext で表示される。`definesPresentationContext: true` を持つ最も近い祖先 view controller の bounds 内に重なる挙動だが、ルート Stack 配下に置くと presentation context はアプリのルート view controller になり、結果 として画面全体 (タブバーごと) を覆ってしまう。これでは `fullScreenModal` と 見た目の差がなくなり、containedModal を使う意味が消える ── 本来は tab content の bounds に収まることを期待する presentation 値なので、ルート配置は推奨されない (観察用)。swipe down では閉じない。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationCurrentContext. The intended behavior is to overlay within the bounds of the closest ancestor view controller that has `definesPresentationContext: true`, but when placed under the root Stack the presentation context becomes the app's root view controller — so it ends up covering the entire screen (including the tab bar). This collapses the visual distinction from `fullScreenModal` and erases the point of using containedModal — since this presentation value is intended to stay within the tab content bounds, the root placement is not recommended (observation only). Swipe down does not dismiss it."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/form-sheet/on-root.tsx:18
msgid "UIModalPresentationFormSheet で表示される。detent (snap point) を任意の数だけ指定可。sheetGrabberVisible で上端のつまみを表示できる。 ルート Stack 配下なのでタブバーを覆ってシートが下から出る形になる (formSheet は通常 modal 同様タブバー上に乗るのが期待される挙動)。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationFormSheet. Any number of detents (snap points) can be configured. `sheetGrabberVisible` shows the grabber at the top. Since it sits under the root Stack, the sheet rises from the bottom covering the tab bar (formSheet is generally expected to sit above the tab bar, the same as a modal)."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/form-sheet/in-tab.tsx:24
msgid "UIModalPresentationFormSheet で表示される。タブ内 Stack 配下に置いても iOS の formSheet は UIKit 上の最前面に出るため、タブバーを覆って表示される (on-root 版とほぼ同じ見た目)。detent (snap point) や sheetGrabberVisible の挙動は配置に依存しない。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationFormSheet. Even when placed under the in-tab Stack, iOS's formSheet comes up at the front of UIKit's hierarchy, so it covers the tab bar (visually nearly identical to the on-root variant). Detents (snap points) and `sheetGrabberVisible` behavior do not depend on placement."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/in-tab-slide-from-bottom.tsx:16
msgid "UIModalPresentationFullScreen で画面全体を覆う。`animation: slide_from_bottom` を 指定すると下から上にスライドして全画面を覆う。`gestureEnabled: false` のため swipe では 閉じられず、明示的な閉じる操作が必須。"
msgstr "Covers the entire screen with UIModalPresentationFullScreen. Specifying `animation: slide_from_bottom` makes it slide up from the bottom to cover the full screen. Because `gestureEnabled: false`, it cannot be dismissed by swipe and an explicit dismiss action is required."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/on-root-slide-from-bottom.tsx:18
msgid "UIModalPresentationFullScreen で画面全体を覆う。`animation: slide_from_bottom` を 指定すると下から上にスライドして全画面を覆う。ルート Stack 配下の標準挙動。 `gestureEnabled: false` のため swipe では閉じられず、明示的な閉じる操作が必須。"
msgstr "Covers the entire screen using UIModalPresentationFullScreen. Setting `animation: slide_from_bottom` makes it slide up from the bottom while covering the full screen — the standard behavior under the root Stack. Because `gestureEnabled: false` is set, swipe cannot dismiss it; an explicit close action is required."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/on-root.tsx:18
msgid "UIModalPresentationFullScreen で画面全体を覆う。`containedModal` が presentation context の bounds 内に収まるのに対し、`fullScreenModal` は presentation context に関係なく画面全体を覆う。ルート Stack 配下に置いた場合の標準挙動。 React Navigation 公式に「ジェスチャーで dismiss できない」と明記されているため (`A screen using this presentation style cannot be dismissed by gesture.`)、swipe で閉じない挙動はライブラリの保証として依拠できる。明示的な閉じる操作が必須。"
msgstr "Covers the entire screen with UIModalPresentationFullScreen. Whereas `containedModal` stays within the bounds of the presentation context, `fullScreenModal` covers the full screen regardless of presentation context. This is the standard behavior when placed under the root Stack. React Navigation documents \"A screen using this presentation style cannot be dismissed by gesture.\", so the no-swipe behavior is a library-level guarantee you can rely on. An explicit dismiss action is required."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal/in-tab.tsx:16
msgid "UIModalPresentationFullScreen で画面全体を覆う。`fullScreenModal` は presentation context に関係なく画面全体を覆うので、タブ内 Stack 配下に置いてもタブバーごと 画面全体を覆う (on-root 版と iOS では同じ見た目になる)。React Navigation 公式に「ジェスチャーで dismiss できない」と明記されているため、swipe で閉じない挙動はライブラリの保証として依拠できる。明示的な閉じる操作が必須。"
msgstr "Covers the entire screen with UIModalPresentationFullScreen. Since `fullScreenModal` covers the full screen regardless of presentation context, even when placed under the in-tab Stack it still covers the entire screen including the tab bar (visually identical to the on-root variant on iOS). React Navigation documents that it cannot be dismissed by gesture, so the no-swipe behavior is a library-level guarantee. An explicit dismiss action is required."

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/contained-transparent-modal/in-tab.tsx:16
msgid "UIModalPresentationOverCurrentContext で表示される。透過を保ったまま current context の上に重なる。本サンプルはホームタブの内側 Stack 配下に配置しているため、開いても current context の範囲 (タブバーを除いた tab content 領域) に透過オーバーレイが 収まる ── これが containedTransparentModal の本来期待される挙動。タブバーは前面に 残ったままになる。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationOverCurrentContext. Overlays the current context while remaining transparent. This sample is placed under the in-tab Stack on the Home tab, so the transparent overlay stays within the current context's bounds (the tab content area, excluding the tab bar) — this is the originally expected behavior of containedTransparentModal. The tab bar remains in front."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/contained-transparent-modal/on-root.tsx:16
msgid "UIModalPresentationOverCurrentContext で表示される。透過を保ったまま current context の上に重なる挙動だが、ルート Stack 配下に置くと current context はアプリのルート view controller になり、結果として画面全体 (タブバーを含む領域全体) に透過オーバーレイが展開してしまう。これでは `transparentModal` と見た目の差が なくなり、containedTransparentModal を使う意味が消える ── 本来は tab content の bounds に収まることを期待する presentation 値なので、ルート配置は推奨されない (観察用)。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationOverCurrentContext. The intended behavior is to overlay the current context transparently, but when placed under the root Stack the current context becomes the app's root view controller — so the transparent overlay ends up spanning the entire screen (including the tab bar area). This collapses the visual distinction from `transparentModal` and erases the point of using containedTransparentModal — since this presentation value is intended to stay within the tab content bounds, the root placement is not recommended (observation only)."

